text: Renovell Nichel from the LIRMM-CNRS, Montpellier Cedex, Herault, France was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for contributions to failure analysis and to defect-oriented tests of digital and analog circuits and systems. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:French electrical engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
